and claim adjustment expense reestimated as of subsequent years less net reserves recorded at the end of the year, as originally estimated) for years prior to 2004 relates only to losses recorded by
tpc and does not include reserve development recorded by spc. for 2004 and subsequent years, includes spc reserves and subsequent development recorded by spc. at december31, 2004, spc gross
